  "text": "Despite these and other objections, CDC/NIOSH issued its final report in December 1980. Without even notifying the committee, it submitted a much shorter version to The Lancet that was published on January 31, 1981 [CITATION_1] . On January 26, 1981 (and without knowledge of the publication), Dr. Bross submitted a critique to CDC/ NIOSH, \"Radiogenic Lung Cancer Among Nuclear Workers at Portsmouth Naval Shipyard\" which noted in the public record that:",
